    "name": "SEAL",
    "description": "A new method is proposed to learn link prediction heuristics from local subgraphs using a graph neural network (GNN). This approach is based on the developed $\\gamma$-decaying heuristic theory and aims to automatically learn a heuristic that suits the current network. Experimental results indicate this GNN model shows unprecedented performance, working consistently well across a wide range of problems.",
